data.name: B_BrowsePathToHLC2V.ToolTip
data.value: You need provide C2V from any Sentinel HL Driverless key (maybe HASP all right too, but not tested) except Sentinel HL Basic and Sentinel HL Net / Sentinel HL Net Time model for current Batch code, because MK Cleaner need create network license for HL key for subtract the license from the Master key.
